Title : Wikipedia:WikiProject Opera/SotM/August2014
Text : [[File:Serafino Gentili by Luigi Rados (1773 - 1840).jpg|right|100px]]
'''The Opera of the Month for August is Rossini's ''[[L'italiana in Algeri]]''. This year marks the 201st anniversary of its premiere.'''

We need articles on...
*[[Serafino Gentili]] ''(pictured)'', who created the role of Lindoro 
*[[Paolo Rosich]], who created the role of Taddeo as well as Buralicchio in ''[[L'equivoco stravagante]]'' 
*[[Angelo Anelli]], who wrote the libretto for this opera and several operas by other composers.
